About Us - Sky High Water Slides
end half

Here's why we are the Best!
Welcome to Sky High Water Slides, where the fun never stops! With over a decade of expertise in the industry, we bring the joy of bounce houses, giant water slides, and oversized obstacle courses, party tents, among many other party rentals, right to your doorstep. Our commitment to delivering an unforgettable experience is matched by our stellar 5-star rating on Google.
At Sky High Water Slides, we understand what you're looking for – the best value for your dollar and the assurance of partnering with a reliable company. As your go-to party rental service in Brevard County, we take pride in ensuring your event is a smashing success, being there for you every step of the way.
Safety is our top priority. We exclusively source new inflatables in bulk directly from the manufacturer, equipped with cutting-edge features like "no jump" netting and large bumper barriers, ensuring your children's safety. Our units are always clean and sanitized upon delivery.
Expect a hassle-free experience from start to finish. Our setup service is swift and efficient, leaving you worry-free and ready to enjoy the festivities. At Sky High Water Slides, we believe in transparent communication ahead of time & ensuring your questions are answered comprehensively before we leave on set-up day. Booking with us means more than just renting equipment – it's a seamless process where our team is dedicated to crafting the best possible event for you.
Join the countless customers who rave about their Sky High experience, making Monday mornings the perfect opportunity to share your weekend excitement with coworkers. Let's turn your event into a celebration to remember – choose Sky High Water Slides for unparalleled fun and friendly service!
